thread.title: anon@nottingham
thread.title_full: Car Hire Labs bewertet von anon@nottingham

author: anon@nottingham
title: anon@nottingham
text: Easy to use and good price but unclear until after payment that the final payment to the supplier on collection would be in Euro, where the total payable throughtout the booking process was in UK Pounds. The exchange rate used to calculate the UK price from the start wasn't representitave of one my bank will give me when I collect the car, so slightly more than led to believe.
